 |title2       = "Lord Tell Me Why"
 |description2 = The rhythmic, [[gospel music|gospel]]-styled song is about a lower class White man's disillusionment. It was co-written by drummer [[Jim Keltner]].<ref name="liner"/>
 |filename3    = Cooder - Dreamer.ogg  
